{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-single-page-js","path":"/symbology/","result":{"data":{"page":{"title":"Symbology","content":"\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-primary-color has-text-color\">LUV is a dynamic, entangled, unzipped matrix of performance, premonition, and praxis &#8230; a diorama encasing the heart, leaf, spaceship, firefly, hummingbird &amp; ankh, symbols that advance its plot. The symbols are an interface where the framework of one artist ends and that of another begins. This symbology is constructed from limited viewpoints and experiences—a mosaic of opposing accuracies—that segue between individual and collective.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><span class=\"wp-image-6338 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:76px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/fb376/Luv_Symbol-1.png 19w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/42373/Luv_Symbol-1.png 38w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/91a96/Luv_Symbol-1.png 76w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/f922f/Luv_Symbol-1.png 114w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/0691c/Luv_Symbol-1.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcSet=\"/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/fb376/Luv_Symbol-1.png 19w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/42373/Luv_Symbol-1.png 38w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/91a96/Luv_Symbol-1.png 76w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/f922f/Luv_Symbol-1.png 114w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/0691c/Luv_Symbol-1.png 151w\" src=\"/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/91a96/Luv_Symbol-1.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/fb376/Luv_Symbol-1.png 19w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/42373/Luv_Symbol-1.png 38w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/91a96/Luv_Symbol-1.png 76w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/f922f/Luv_Symbol-1.png 114w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/0691c/Luv_Symbol-1.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcset=\"/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/fb376/Luv_Symbol-1.png 19w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/42373/Luv_Symbol-1.png 38w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/91a96/Luv_Symbol-1.png 76w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/f922f/Luv_Symbol-1.png 114w,\n/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/0691c/Luv_Symbol-1.png 151w\" src=\"/static/eb445ec33338bd21eb90e761e2e559e3/91a96/Luv_Symbol-1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-primary-color has-text-color\">The HEART symbol came first. It was carved into a tree at the same time as the words, Luv ‘til it Hurts. The spelling of luv was changed forever, and the buxom HEART became a megaphone&#8211;pumping loudly and emitting reverberations. Desirous of speed, its incumbent pangs, swarm-like, fragment into projectiles before taking flight.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><span class=\"wp-image-6352 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:76px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/fb376/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 19w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/42373/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 38w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/91a96/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 76w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/f922f/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 114w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/0691c/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcSet=\"/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/fb376/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 19w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/42373/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 38w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/91a96/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 76w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/f922f/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 114w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/0691c/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 151w\" src=\"/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/91a96/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/fb376/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 19w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/42373/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 38w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/91a96/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 76w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/f922f/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 114w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/0691c/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcset=\"/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/fb376/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 19w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/42373/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 38w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/91a96/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 76w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/f922f/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 114w,\n/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/0691c/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png 151w\" src=\"/static/c13b8cb6b2e1c3178ee9aed7fe2d57d9/91a96/Luv_Symbol-2-1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-primary-color has-text-color\">Some are docile like a LEAF, swaying not so far from the tree as it plummets and alights akimbo atop the galaxy.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><span class=\"wp-image-6360 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:76px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/fb376/Luv_Symbol-3.png 19w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/42373/Luv_Symbol-3.png 38w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/91a96/Luv_Symbol-3.png 76w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/f922f/Luv_Symbol-3.png 114w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/0691c/Luv_Symbol-3.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcSet=\"/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/fb376/Luv_Symbol-3.png 19w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/42373/Luv_Symbol-3.png 38w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/91a96/Luv_Symbol-3.png 76w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/f922f/Luv_Symbol-3.png 114w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/0691c/Luv_Symbol-3.png 151w\" src=\"/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/91a96/Luv_Symbol-3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/fb376/Luv_Symbol-3.png 19w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/42373/Luv_Symbol-3.png 38w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/91a96/Luv_Symbol-3.png 76w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/f922f/Luv_Symbol-3.png 114w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/0691c/Luv_Symbol-3.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcset=\"/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/fb376/Luv_Symbol-3.png 19w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/42373/Luv_Symbol-3.png 38w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/91a96/Luv_Symbol-3.png 76w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/f922f/Luv_Symbol-3.png 114w,\n/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/0691c/Luv_Symbol-3.png 151w\" src=\"/static/1d9624ef42184e7ab931b30b788a9c12/91a96/Luv_Symbol-3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-primary-color has-text-color\">Confused for magic carpets, an armada of over 300 leaves is best seen from one spectacular SPACESHIP with a glass-bottom viewing deck (license no. 00-1986).</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><span class=\"wp-image-6364 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:76px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/fb376/Luv_Symbol-4.png 19w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/42373/Luv_Symbol-4.png 38w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/91a96/Luv_Symbol-4.png 76w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/f922f/Luv_Symbol-4.png 114w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/0691c/Luv_Symbol-4.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcSet=\"/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/fb376/Luv_Symbol-4.png 19w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/42373/Luv_Symbol-4.png 38w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/91a96/Luv_Symbol-4.png 76w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/f922f/Luv_Symbol-4.png 114w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/0691c/Luv_Symbol-4.png 151w\" src=\"/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/91a96/Luv_Symbol-4.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/fb376/Luv_Symbol-4.png 19w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/42373/Luv_Symbol-4.png 38w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/91a96/Luv_Symbol-4.png 76w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/f922f/Luv_Symbol-4.png 114w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/0691c/Luv_Symbol-4.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcset=\"/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/fb376/Luv_Symbol-4.png 19w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/42373/Luv_Symbol-4.png 38w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/91a96/Luv_Symbol-4.png 76w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/f922f/Luv_Symbol-4.png 114w,\n/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/0691c/Luv_Symbol-4.png 151w\" src=\"/static/9105c86e381e821c5978c19b89d06d0e/91a96/Luv_Symbol-4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-primary-color has-text-color\">Small hovercraft break off the mothership, attached only by bloody umbilica … offal burns off at light-speed to reveal dart-shaped poetics with bright, anti-venom tips and soft names in each language: luciérnaga, vagalume, FIREFLY.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><span class=\"wp-image-6368 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:76px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/fb376/Luv_Symbol-5.png 19w,\n/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/42373/Luv_Symbol-5.png 38w,\n/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/91a96/Luv_Symbol-5.png 76w,\n/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/f922f/Luv_Symbol-5.png 114w,\n/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/0691c/Luv_Symbol-5.png 151w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 76px) 100vw, 76px\" srcSet=\"/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/fb376/Luv_Symbol-5.png 19w,\n/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/42373/Luv_Symbol-5.png 38w,\n/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/91a96/Luv_Symbol-5.png 76w,\n/static/a27d42eaeaa4169aa090b97b5ebabff3/f922f/Luv_Symbol-5.png 114w,\n/static/a2